The diameter is approximately 2 3/4 inches and it is approximately 1 7/8 inches tall.

*Your tiara will be made to order within approximately 1-4 days.*
 
Orders ship from Washington state (USA). 
Orders shipping to the United States will be shipped via USPS First Class Mail (estimated delivery 2-5 business days). Orders shipping to all other countries will be shipped via USPS First Class Mail (delivery timeframes vary).

Rush orders/shipping are available. There is a $5 rush fee plus your shipping fee may be increased based on your needs. Please contact us with your specific needs.

Please "LIKE" our Facebook page to see our specials and new crowns: 

www.facebook.com/handcraftedcrowns 

We would love it if you would PIN our photos! 

All unmarked photos © Handcrafted Crowns
